      <div class="seven-lines-inner">
        <div class="seven-lines-header">THE SEVEN LINES</div>
        <div class="seven-lines-note">Click any line to read the full tenet</div>
        <ol class="seven-lines-list">
          <li class="seven-lines-item" onclick="jumpToTenet(1)">
            <span class="seven-lines-num">1</span>
            <span class="seven-lines-text">What disturbs you is never the event — it is what you make of it.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="seven-lines-item" onclick="jumpToTenet(2)">
            <span class="seven-lines-num">2</span>
            <span class="seven-lines-text">It is not the losing that hurts most — it is the grip.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="seven-lines-item" onclick="jumpToTenet(3)">
            <span class="seven-lines-num">3</span>
            <span class="seven-lines-text">The wall between you and everything else is thinner than you think.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="seven-lines-item" onclick="jumpToTenet(4)">
            <span class="seven-lines-num">4</span>
            <span class="seven-lines-text">You can only ever be here. Everything else is memory or invention.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="seven-lines-item" onclick="jumpToTenet(5)">
            <span class="seven-lines-num">5</span>
            <span class="seven-lines-text">You are not what you intend. You are what you do when it costs something.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="seven-lines-item" onclick="jumpToTenet(6)">
            <span class="seven-lines-num">6</span>
            <span class="seven-lines-text">You will not find your purpose. You will build it.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="seven-lines-item" onclick="jumpToTenet(7)">
            <span class="seven-lines-num">7</span>
            <span class="seven-lines-text">The need to be right, to be seen, to be safe — that is what stands between you and clarity.</span>
          </li>
